Jira Usage Guidance
📌 Follow these steps to get started with Jira in this app:

Connect to Jira

Go to the Jira Connection screen.

Enter your Jira username and password.

Click Connect ✅.

View Your Projects

Favourite Projects Tab → Shows projects you have already marked as favourite.

All Projects Tab → Shows all projects you have access to.

Mark a Project as Favourite

In the All Projects tab, click ⭐ next to a project to mark it as favourite.

It will now appear in your Favourite Projects tab.

Ask Questions on Favourite Projects

With a Jira Ticket → Select a favourite project, pick a Jira ticket, and ask your question.

Without a Jira Ticket → Select a favourite project and ask a question directly.












